<p style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt">Weatherford ISD is committed to the health, safety and academic learning of your child. Based on recommendations from health officials, Weatherford ISD will be closed for the remainder of the 2019-2020 school year to disrupt widespread infection of COVID-19.</span></p>
<p style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; color: #212121"> </span></p>
<p style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; color: #212121">To view the different Weatherford ISD resources available to you, including Learning at Home materials, please <strong><a href="https://sites.google.com/weatherfordisd.com/wisd-school-closure/home" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span style="color: blue">click HERE</span></a></strong> . </span></p>
<p style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; color: #212121"> </span></p>
<p style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; color: #212121">Please check back often as we will continue to update.</span></strong></p>
</div>
