	<div class="page-block page-block-text">
			<div class="placeholder-tinymce-text"><strong>Meal Pick Up for Children 18 and Younger</strong></div>
<div class="placeholder-tinymce-text"> </div>
<div class="placeholder-tinymce-text">
<p style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px">Beginning Monday, March 23, the Weatherford ISD Child Nutrition Department will begin offering free breakfast and lunch to children 18 and under at two campus locations. Pedestrian traffic at Ikard is discouraged due to safety concerns for students walking on Bankhead Highway. For the health and safety of our families and staff, food will be delivered in a drive through format with no onsite dining. Under current Texas Department of Agriculture guidelines, meal service may only be provided to students who are present.</p>
<p style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px"> </p>
<p style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 0.5in; padding: 0px"><strong>Meal Pick Up Locations: </strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 0.5in; padding: 0px">Curtis Elementary                                            Ikard Elementary</p>
<p style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 0.5in; padding: 0px">501 W. Russell Street                                     100 Ikard Lane</p>
<p style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 0.5in; padding: 0px"> </p>
<p style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 0.5in; padding: 0px"><strong>Serving Days and Times:</strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 0.5in; padding: 0px">11:00 am - 1:00 pm on Mondays and Wednesdays</p>
<p style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 0.5in; padding: 0px"><em>Breakfast and lunch will be given at the same time. <br>Meals for 2 days will be given on Mondays; Meals for 3 days will be given on Wednesdays.</em></p>
<p style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 0.5in; padding: 0px"> </p>
<p style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 0.5in; padding: 0px"><strong><span style="color: #cf000f"><em>Please note there will be no meals given out on a scheduled school holiday on Monday, April 20, 2020. </em></span></strong></p>
</div>
